('6622f2974df79', 'First Tech Challenge - Lyon', 'This is our first participation in the First Tech Challenge (FTC) which is organized for only the second time by [Robotique FIRST France](https://robotiquefirstfrance.org/ftc/) in Lyon.\nThe rules are briefly outlined here: \n<center><iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/6e-5Uo1dRic?si=OTt1S-JNfMcyMN_e\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer;clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe></center>\n\nWe have been preparing for this competition since December.\n<center>\n    <table>\n        <tr>\n            <td><img src=\"/proxyPhotos?code=blog/bob-ross/66223617b2c05/50.jpg\"></td>\n            <td><img src=\"/proxyPhotos?code=blog/bob-ross/662236118f729/50.jpg\"></td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td><img src=\"/proxyPhotos?code=blog/bob-ross/6622361dd611c/50.jpg\"></td>\n            <td><img src=\"/proxyPhotos?code=blog/bob-ross/66223624050e1/50.jpg\"></td>\n        </tr>\n    </table>\n</center>\n\nOur organization into two teams: one for the robot design and the other for its programming was not up to our expectations. The first took a lot of time, leaving too little for the latter. Before arriving in Lyon, we are still very behind!\n\nOur team now has an official FTC competition number: #25133\n\nIt is composed of:\n * Aurélien\n * Elina\n * Hadrien\n * Pierrick\n * Quentin\n * Timothé\n\n coached by Mohamed, Matthieu, François, and Franck.\n\nWe are supported by a team of wonderful parents, some of whom accompany us on our trip to Lyon.\n\nWe arrive a bit before the opening and take the opportunity to visit the [INSA fablab](https://fablab-fabriqueinnovation.fr/).\n\n<center>\n    <table>\n        <tr>\n            <td><img src=\"/proxyPhotos?code=blog/bob-ross/662236304b563/50.jpg\"></td>\n            <td><img src=\"/proxyPhotos?code=blog/bob-ross/662239fe2b656/50.jpg\"></td>\n        </tr>\n    </table>\n</center>\n\nThe first day is mostly devoted to a few administrative formalities, including the usual robot inspection.\n\n<center><img src=\"/proxyPhotos?code=blog/bob-ross/662236366e895/50.jpg\"></center>\n\nHowever, we realize that a crucial point of the game rules had escaped us: we are not allowed to carry more than two *pixels* at a time! Bad luck because our strategy was precisely based on catching as many as possible at once! We urgently need to review it.\n\n<center><img src=\"/proxyPhotos?code=blog/bob-ross/6622363c91fc0/50.jpg\"></center>\n\nAfter a good meal all together, we go to bed, exhausted, as the competition starts at 8 AM the next day.\n\nAnd we are ready! All dressed up like in Singapore, we look great :smile: \n\n<center><img src=\"/proxyPhotos?code=blog/bob-ross/66223642b4f65/50.jpg\"></center>\n\nOur first match shows us our first weaknesses:\n<center>\n    <iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/nfpl8OMUD4w?si=Luh_dqiN8cQKoUPp&amp;start=5454\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</center>\n\nThanks to the allied team we win this match but we absolutely need to improve our robot.\n\n<center>\n    <table>\n        <tr>\n            <td><img src=\"/proxyPhotos?code=blog/bob-ross/66223ebeb568c/50.jpg\"></td>\n            <td><img src=\"/proxyPhotos?code=blog/bob-ross/66223eb8926d7/50.jpg\"></td>\n        </tr>\n    </table>\n</center>\n\nWe don&lrsquo;t get discouraged, but our second match has a bad surprise for us.\n\n<center>\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/nfpl8OMUD4w?si=zDdzRCmIWtfl42WE&amp;start=9779\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer;  clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</center>\n\nAfter messing up during the autonomous period, the battery disconnects and there&lrsquo;s no way to control the robot.\nBack to the stand, and securing the battery connector. We also try to fine-tune the drone launcher.\n<center><img src=\"/proxyPhotos?code=blog/bob-ross/66223eb26f486/50.jpg\"></center>\n\nThen we define an original strategy with our future allies: They have a robot capable of correctly placing the *pixels*, we offer to bring them to them.\n\n<center><iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/nfpl8OMUD4w?si=3tqBZHmomar7j7xl&amp;start=13371\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe></center>\n\nThe strategy is respected and works, but our robot is hard to handle, and our opponents hinder us twice, preventing us from hanging at the end. The launcher worked super well and granted us the maximum points: 30! It&lrsquo;s progressing.\n\nIt&lrsquo;s mealtime which we devour because there&lrsquo;s still work to do, especially on the programming and fine-tuning of the launcher.\n\n<center>\n    <table>\n        <tr>\n            <td><img src=\"/proxyPhotos?code=blog/bob-ross/66223648d818d/50.jpg\"></td>\n            <td><img src=\"/proxyPhotos?code=blog/bob-ross/6622362a283e6/50.jpg\"></td>\n        </tr>\n    </table>\n</center>\n\nAnd then we go back with the same strategy but we have fixed the piloting problem:\n\n<center><iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/nfpl8OMUD4w?si=hUV63Xm3gKT1gvL9&amp;start=21794\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe></center>\n\nFinally a great success, our robot hangs on at the end of the match. It has been capable of doing it from the beginning but other technical issues have always prevented it. What pride!\n\n<center><img src=\"/proxyPhotos?code=blog/bob-ross/6622365b4da9f/50.jpg\"></center>\n\nOf course, our ranking isn&lrsquo;t great and our next allies are even worse ranked than us! However, our opponents are not formidable either and our robot is starting to have serious assets. We decide to try to place the *pixels* on the *backdrop* ourselves rather than serving our allies. On the other hand, we have given up the autonomous period.\nLast match:\n<center><iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/nfpl8OMUD4w?si=4drc_eo5w4TBAGjW&amp;start=30845\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer;  clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe></center>\n\nAnd it&lrsquo;s finally good! Although the *pixels* were placed next to the plate, the piloting is royal. Our robot is able to go get new ones, drop them in the *backstage*, then it turns around, sends the drone into zone 2 (20 points) and holds everyone in suspense at the time of hanging, managing it only at the very last second. What a match.\n:100: points won by our alliance, almost thanks to us this time. We finish this competition on a positive note although the final ranking is only 37th out of 54 teams.\n\n<center><img src=\"/proxyPhotos?code=blog/bob-ross/6622364f076d3/50.jpg\"></center>\n\n<center> <h2>Looking forward to the next one!</h2></center>\n', 'first-tech-challenge-lyon', '/proxyPhotos?code=blog/bob-ross/6622a1cf3e578/50.png', 'en', '6622a426b9724', 'This is our first participation in the First Tech Challenge (FTC) which is organized for only the second time by [Robotique FIRST France](https://robo', NULL, '2024-04-19 15:04:38', '2024-04-20 00:39:19', NULL, NULL),
('66351ba1db69a', 'FIRST Global TEAM FRANCE à Athènes : We Robot se lance dans la compétition ! ', '## We Robot a été pour la troisième fois sélectionnée pour représenter officiellement la France au <i>FIRST</i> Global Challenge, compétition de robotique qui réunit chaque année de jeunes passionnés du monde entier avec plus de 190 pays représentés. \n\nLa 8ème édition de la compétition se déroule cette année à Athènes, du 26 au 29 septembre 2024.\n\n<iframe class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"1060\" height=\"597\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/MAF51J53uoE?\nversion=3&amp;rel=1&amp;showsearch=0&amp;showinfo=1&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;fs=1&amp;hl=fr-FR&amp;autohide=2&amp;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe>\n \nCe nouveau défi est une belle opportunité pour notre équipe de monter en compétences, mener un projet, le tout en prenant un maximum de plaisir ! Notre équipe est toujours aussi motivée pour relever ce challenge ! Elle a récemment accueilli de nouveaux membres, pour pousser la qualité des travaux et l’esprit d’équipe toujours plus haut !\n\n<center>\n<table>\n    <tr>\n        <td><img src=\"/proxyPhotos?code=blog/bob-ross/663bcd683a3f0/75.png\" alt=\"Bob Ross\"></td>\n    </tr>\n</table>\n</center>\n\nPour mener à bien ce projet et le concrétiser, We Robot est à la recherche de sponsors. Vous aussi prenez part à la grande aventure du <i>FIRST</i> Global Challenge en nous soutenant ! Vous pouvez nous soutenir ici :\n<!--hyperlien vers une page Web-->\n<a href=\"https://www.helloasso.com/associations/we-robot/formulaires/1\"\n   title=\"soutenir We Robot\">  \n\nFaire un don à WE ROBOT (helloasso.com)\n</a>\n\n<center>\n<div style=\"width: 200px\">\n<img src=\"/proxyPhotos?code=blog/bob-ross/6509b99fa50d9/50.jpg\">\n</div>\n</center>\n', 'first-global-team-france-a-athenes-we-robot-se-lance-dans-la-competition', '/proxyPhotos?code=blog/bob-ross/6634ff59aab60/50.jpg', 'fr', '66351ba1db83c', 'Nous sommes officiellement sélectionnés pour représenter la France aux 8ème « Jeux Olympiques » de la robotique du FIRST Global Challenge à Athènes du 26 au 29 septembre 2024', NULL, '2024-05-02 13:15:13', '2024-05-12 10:21:08', NULL, NULL),
('6635234a0916d', 'First Global Team France in Athens : We Robot enters the competition! ', '## We Robot has been selected for the third time to officially represent France at the FIRST Global Challenge, a robotics competition that brings together young enthusiasts from all over the world every year, with over 190 countries represented. \n\nThe 8th edition of the competition takes place this year in Athens, from September 26 to 29, 2024.\n\n\n<center>\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/MAF51J53uoE?si=M3jRboD9PUNYK6xH\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</center>\n \n\n\nThis new challenge is a great opportunity for our team to improve their skills, lead a project, and have a lot of fun in the process ! Our team is as motivated as ever to take up this challenge ! We&lrsquo;ve recently welcomed a number of new members, to help us push the quality of our work and our team spirit to new heights !\n\n\n<center>\n<img src=\"/proxyPhotos?code=blog/bob-ross/654bc47831545/50.jpg\">\n</div>\n</center>\n\n\n\nTo bring this project to fruition, We Robot is looking for sponsors. You too can take part in the FIRST Global Challenge adventure by supporting us ! You can support us here :\n<!--hyperlien vers une page Web-->\n<a href=\"https://www.helloasso.com/associations/we-robot/formulaires/1\"\n   title=\"support We Robot\">  \n\nSupport WE ROBOT (helloasso.com)\n</a>\n\n<center>\n<div style=\"width: 200px\">\n<img src=\"/proxyPhotos?code=blog/bob-ross/6509b99fa50d9/50.jpg\">\n</div>\n</center>', 'first-global-team-france-in-athens-we-robot-enters-the-competition', '/proxyPhotos?code=blog/bob-ross/66351ea1a662d/50.jpg', 'en', '6635234a09275', '## We Robot has been selected for the third time to officially represent France at the FIRST Global Challenge, a robotics competition that brings toge', NULL, '2024-05-03 19:47:54', '2024-05-03 19:47:54', NULL, NULL),
('663bc03ac5304', 'Les valeurs de la TEAM FRANCE', '<iframe class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"1060\" height=\"597\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/HdcyzBC6NDw?version=3&amp;rel=1&amp;showsearch=0&amp;showinfo=1&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;fs=1&amp;hl=fr-FR&amp;autohide=2&amp;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe>\n\n<p>La TEAM FRANCE partage les objectifs port&eacute;s par Dean Kamen et sa fondation <i>FIRST</i> depuis 1989 :</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Nous sommes une communaut&eacute; d&eacute;di&eacute;e &agrave; la poursuite coop&eacute;rative d&lrsquo;un monde plus paisible, r&eacute;alis&eacute; en innovant ensemble pour garantir la vie, la libert&eacute;, le succ&egrave;s, l&lrsquo;avancement et le bonheur de tous ceux qui partagent notre plan&egrave;te.</li>\n<li>Nous croyons que toutes les personnes ont des dons sp&eacute;ciaux qui les rendent innovateurs. Les probl&egrave;mes de la plan&egrave;te Terre ne peuvent pas &ecirc;tre r&eacute;solus par un individu ou une nation seul(e). Lorsque nous travaillons ensemble, il n&lrsquo;y a rien que nous ne puissions accomplir et nous pouvons partager les avantages de nos nouvelles inventions avec le monde entier.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<table border=\"1\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%;\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: right;\"><img src=\"/proxyPhotos?code=blog/bob-ross/663bc0653f908/50.jpg\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" alt=\"\" style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" /></td>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">\n<h2><strong>Dean Kamen</strong></h2>\n<p>Cr&eacute;ateur de la fondation <i>FIRST<br /></i>Inventeur du gyropode Segway</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><i>&laquo;&nbsp;Le FIRST </i>Global <i>Challenge d&eacute;montre le formidable pouvoir de la technologie, de l&lrsquo;&eacute;ducation et de la comp&eacute;tition pour&nbsp;rassembler la prochaine g&eacute;n&eacute;ration&nbsp;d&lrsquo;innovateurs &raquo;</i></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>LA TEAM FRANCE est en harmonie avec les moyens mis en avant par la fondation <i>FIRST</i> :</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Nous promouvons la paix en travaillant ensemble sur des projets scientifiques et technologiques. Ces initiatives favorisent la compr&eacute;hension commune et les exp&eacute;riences partag&eacute;es.</li>\n<li>Nous traitons tout le monde avec gentillesse et respect inconditionnels. L&lrsquo;empathie et le travail acharn&eacute; sont les piliers du progr&egrave;s.</li>\n<li>Nous reconnaissons les contributions des autres. Nous apprenons davantage les uns des autres que seuls.</li>\n<li>Nous croyons que le monde n&lrsquo;a pas besoin de perdants pour avoir des gagnants. Le succ&egrave;s d&lrsquo;une personne ne conduit pas in&eacute;vitablement &agrave; la perte d&lrsquo;une autre. Au contraire, les innovations partag&eacute;es peuvent apporter &agrave; la fois des r&eacute;compenses aux innovateurs et une meilleure qualit&eacute; de vie pour toutes et tous.</li>\n<li>Nous promouvons l&lrsquo;apprentissage et la cr&eacute;ativit&eacute; dans nos communaut&eacute;s, nos nations et notre monde. L&lrsquo;imagination et la technologie sont des outils essentiels pour construire un avenir meilleur.</li>\n<li>Nous travaillons pour garantir que notre propre progr&egrave;s n&lrsquo;inhibe pas les autres. Aucun d&lrsquo;entre nous ne peut r&eacute;ussir au d&eacute;triment de nos concitoyens.</li>\n<li>Nous aimons ce que nous faisons. Nous le partageons avec d&lrsquo;autres et, ce faisant, nous stimulons non seulement notre innovation, mais nous apportons &eacute;galement la paix gr&acirc;ce &agrave; la collaboration.</li>\n</ul>', 'les-valeurs-de-la-team-france', '/proxyPhotos?code=blog/bob-ross/663b5d1e8d3b1/50.jpg', 'fr', '663bc03ac54e0', 'La TEAM FRANCE partage les objectifs portés par Dean Kamen et sa fondation FIRST depuis 1989 ', NULL, '2024-05-07 14:00:00', '2024-05-08 20:50:35', NULL, NULL),
('663bd20a19923', 'FIRST Global TEAM FRANCE in Athens : We Robot takes on the competition !', '\"We Robot\" has been selected for the third time to officially represent France at the <i>FIRST</i> Global Challenge, a robotics competition that brings together young enthusiasts from around the world, with over 190 countries participating.\n\n\n\nThe 8th edition of the competition is taking place this year in Athens, from September 26th to 29th, 2024.\n\n<iframe class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"1060\" height=\"597\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/MAF51J53uoE?\nversion=3&amp;rel=1&amp;showsearch=0&amp;showinfo=1&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;fs=1&amp;hl=fr-FR&amp;autohide=2&amp;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe>\n\nThis new challenge is a great opportunity for our team to enhance our skills, lead a project, all while enjoying ourselves to the fullest ! Our team is as motivated as ever to take on this challenge ! We have recently welcomed new members to push the quality of work and team spirit even higher !\n\n<center>\n<table>\n    <tr>\n        <td><img src=\"/proxyPhotos?code=blog/bob-ross/663bcd683a3f0/75.png\" alt=\"Bob Ross\"></td>\n    </tr>\n</table>\n</center>\n\nTo successfully carry out this project and make it a reality, We Robot is looking for sponsors. Join the great adventure of the <i>FIRST </i>Global Challenge by supporting us! You can support us here :\n\n<a href=\"https://www.helloasso.com/associations/we-robot/formulaires/1\"\n   title=\"soutenir We Robot\">  \n\nTo make a donation to WE ROBOT (helloasso.com)\n</a>\n\n<center>\n<div style=\"width: 200px\">\n<img src=\"/proxyPhotos?code=blog/bob-ross/6509b99fa50d9/50.jpg\">\n</div>\n</center>\n\n\n\n', 'first-global-team-france-in-athens-we-robot-takes-on-the-competition', '/proxyPhotos?code=blog/bob-ross/6634ff59aab60/50.jpg', 'en', '66351ba1db83c', '\"We Robot\" has been selected for the third time to officially represent France at the FIRST Global Challenge, a robotics competition that brings toget', NULL, '2024-05-02 22:00:00', '2024-05-12 10:21:15', NULL, NULL),
('663be0f53aa6a', 'The values of TEAM FRANCE', '<iframe class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"1060\" height=\"597\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/HdcyzBC6NDw?version=3&amp;rel=1&amp;showsearch=0&amp;showinfo=1&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;fs=1&amp;hl=fr-FR&amp;autohide=2&amp;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe>\n\n<p>The TEAM FRANCE shares the goals advocated by Dean Kamen and his foundation <i>FIRST</i> since 1989 :</p>\n<ul>\n<li>We are a community dedicated to the cooperative pursuit of a more peaceful world, achieved by innovating together to ensure the life, freedom, success, advancement, and happiness of all who share our planet.</li>\n<li>We believe that every person has special gifts that make them innovators. The problems of planet Earth cannot be solved by an individual or a single nation alone. When we work together, there is nothing we cannot accomplish, and we can share the benefits of our new inventions with the entire world.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<table border=\"1\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%;\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 50%; text-align: right;\"><img src=\"/proxyPhotos?code=blog/bob-ross/663bc0653f908/50.jpg\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" alt=\"\" style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" /></td>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">\n<h2><strong>Dean Kamen</strong></h2>\n<p>Founder of the <i>FIRST</i> foundation<br /></i>Inventor of the Segway self-balancing scooter</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"<i>\"The FIRST</i> Global<i> Challenge demonstrates the tremendous power of technology, education and competition to assemble the next generation of innovators\"</i></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>TEAM FRANCE aligns with the principles highlighted by the FIRST foundation :</p>\n<ul>\n<li>We promote peace by working together on science and technology projects. These undertakings foster common understanding and experiences.</li>\n<li>We treat everyone with unqualified kindness and respect. Empathy and hard work are the backbone of progress.</li>\n<li>We recognize the contributions of others. We learn more from each other than we do alone.</li>\n<li>We believe that the world does not need losers to have winners. One person’s success does not inevitably lead to another’s loss; instead, shared innovations can bring both rewards to innovators and a greater quality of life for all.</li>\n<li>We promote learning and creativity in our communities, our nations, and our world. Imagination and technology are essential tools to build a better future.</li>\n<li>We work to ensure that our own progress does not inhibit others. None of us can succeed at the expense of our fellow citizens.</li>\n<li>We love what we do. We share it with others and, in so doing, will not only drive our innovation, but also bring peace through collaboration.</li>\n</ul>', 'the-values-of-team-france', '/proxyPhotos?code=blog/bob-ross/663b5d1e8d3b1/50.jpg', 'en', '663bc03ac54e0', '<iframe class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"1060\" height=\"597\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/HdcyzBC6NDw?version=3&amp;rel=1&amp;showsearch=0&amp;showi', NULL, '2024-05-07 08:00:00', '2024-05-08 22:45:50', NULL, NULL),
('663e5f7aac100', 'On cherche des partenaires pour la TEAM FRANCE', '<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><tt><big><small><span style=\"color:#0432FA;\"><strong>La grande nouvelle est tombée le dimanche 4 avril 2024</strong></span></small></big></tt></span></p>\n\n<br>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><tt><small><big><span style=\"color:#0432FA;\">Nous sommes officiellement sélectionnés pour représenter la France aux 8ème « Jeux Olympiques » de la robotique du FIRST Global Challenge à Athènes du 26 au 29 septembre 2024.<br />\n« Ce sera notre troisième participation à ce challenge international et La TEAM FRANCE\nprésentée par We Robot est fière et heureuse d’avoir été sélectionnée avec 190 autres équipes de tous les continents de la planète. Nous nous engageons à donner le meilleur de nous même en faisant fructifier notre expérience »\n</span></big></small></tt></span></p>\n\n<br>\n\n<iframe src=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/19hX-_XkJvoIrtbp3XJ20zgZGFvKw-2-v/preview\" width=\"640\" height=\"936\" allow=\"autoplay\"></iframe>\n', 'on-cherche-des-partenaires-pour-la-team-france', '/proxyPhotos?code=blog/bob-ross/663e5b8473cc2/50.png', 'fr', '663e5f7aac279', 'La TEAM FRANCE présentée par We Robot est officiellement sélectionnée pour le FIRST Global Challenge ATHENS 2024, les Jeux Olympiques junior de la Robotique', NULL, '2024-05-10 07:55:06', '2024-05-10 22:51:04', NULL, NULL),
('663e89ac3b12c', 'We&lrsquo;re looking for partners for TEAM FRANCE', '<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><tt><big><small><span style=\"color:#0432FA;\"><strong>The big news came on Sunday, April 4, 2024</strong></span></small></big></tt></span></p>\n\n<br>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><tt><small><big><span style=\"color:#0432FA;\">We are officially selected to represent France at the 8th FIRST Global Challenge Robotics \"Olympics\" in Athens from September 26-29, 2024.<br />\n\"This will be our third participation in this international challenge, and the TEAM FRANCE presented by We Robot is proud and delighted to have been selected alongside 190 other teams from every continent on the planet. We&lrsquo;re committed to giving it our best shot and making the most of our experience.\"\n</span></big></small></tt></span></p>\n\n<br>\n\n<iframe src=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/19hX-_XkJvoIrtbp3XJ20zgZGFvKw-2-v/preview\" width=\"640\" height=\"936\" allow=\"autoplay\"></iframe>', 'we-re-looking-for-partners-for-team-france', '/proxyPhotos?code=blog/bob-ross/663e5b8473cc2/50.png', 'en', '663e5f7aac279', 'The TEAM FRANCE presented by We Robot is officially selected for the FIRST Global Challenge ATHENS 2024, the Junior Olympic Games of Robotics', NULL, '2024-05-09 23:55:06', '2024-05-10 22:59:31', NULL, NULL),
('663f8526c5459', 'Arrêt sur image à 45 secondes : Timothé figure dans une publication du FIRST Global Challenge !', '## Timothé, un membre de notre équipe, est très récemment apparu dans l’une des dernières vidéos du <i>FIRST</i> Global Challenge visant à faire reconnaître la robotique comme étant un sport officiel. Les images ont été prises lors d’une interview de Timothé qui a eu lieu à Singapour lors de l’édition 2023 du concours.\n\n<center>\n<div style=\"width: 450px\">\n<img src=\"/proxyPhotos?code=blog/bob-ross/663f81637c708/50.jpg\">\n</div>\n</center>\n\n\nUn signe pour notre prochaine participation au  <i>FIRST</i> Global Challenge qui se déroulera du 26 au 29 septembre 2024 à Athènes ? On l’espère ! \nC’est en tous cas une immense fierté pour notre équipe d’apparaître dans une vidéo officielle d’une compétition de robotique internationale comme celle-ci !\n\nLa vidéo avec notre superstar est disponible ici : \n\n\n<center>\n<iframe class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"1060\" height=\"597\" \nsrc=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Ljup-TK_tZY?\nsi=OTt1S-JNfMcyMN_e\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer;clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</center>\n\n<iframe name=\"fitvid-37705\" src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/Ljup-TK_tZY?wmode=transparent\" wmode=\"Opaque\" width=\"805\" height=\"403\" allowfullscreen=\"\" id=\"fitvid339559\"></iframe>\n\n\n\n', 'arret-sur-image-a-45-secondes-timothe-figure-dans-une-publication-du-first-global-challenge', '/proxyPhotos?code=blog/bob-ross/663f81637c708/50.jpg', 'fr', '663f8526c5570', '\nTimothé, un membre de notre équipe est très récemment apparu dans l’une des dernières vidéos du <i>FIRST</i>  Global Challenge visant à faire reconnaître la robotique comme étant un sport officiel.', NULL, '2024-05-11 06:48:06', '2024-05-12 10:19:13', NULL, NULL),
('663f8c23cf5ba', 'Freeze at 45 seconds: Timothé featured in a FIRST Global Challenge publication!', '## \nTimothé, a member of our team, recently appeared in one of the latest  <i>FIRST</i> Global Challenge videos, which aims to have robotics recognized as an official sport. The images were taken during an interview with Timothé that took place in Singapore during the 2023 edition of the competition.\n \n\n<center>\n<div style=\"width: 450px\">\n<img src=\"/proxyPhotos?code=blog/bob-ross/663f81637c708/50.jpg\">\n</div>\n</center>\n\n A sign for our next participation in the <i>FIRST</i> Global Challenge, which will take place from September 26 to 29, 2024 in Athens? We hope so ! \nIn any case, it&lrsquo;s a source of immense pride for our team to appear in an official video of an international robotics competition like this one !\n\nThe video with our superstar is available here : \n\n\n\n\n<iframe class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"1060\" height=\"597\" \nsrc=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Ljup-TK_tZY?\nsi=OTt1S-JNfMcyMN_e\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer;clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe></center>', 'freeze-at-45-seconds-timothe-featured-in-a-first-global-challenge-publication', '/proxyPhotos?code=blog/bob-ross/663f81637c708/50.jpg', 'en', '663f8526c5570', 'Timothé, a member of our team, recently appeared in one of the latest <i>FIRST</i> Global Challenge videos, which aims to have robotics recognized as an official sport. ', NULL, '2024-05-11 12:48:06', '2024-05-11 17:17:55', NULL, NULL);
